      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.8,
        659.72,
        143.93,
        668.72
      ],
      "text": "Overwegingen",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.8,
        670.64,
        515.49,
        679.64
      ],
      "text": "Ten aanzien van uw vraag delen wij het “Uitvoeringsbericht afhandelen verzoek No-riskpolis bij te",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.8,
        681.56,
        520.06,
        690.56
      ],
